00:08:19.280 --> 00:08:26.150
was off duty he was known as a regular at London’s exclusive nightclubs, and was photographed

00:08:26.230 --> 00:08:33.440
arm in arm with a wide variety of eligible young women, earning him the nickname “Randy Andy”.

