Moving into the 2000s, even before the details of Jeffrey Epstein’s crimes became public

00:10:00.200 --> 00:10:07.120
knowledge, Prince Andrew started to see his popularity fade as the scandals started to mount.

00:10:08.380 --> 00:10:14.010
He left the navy in 2001, and was given the title of “Special

00:10:14.010 --> 00:10:17.120
Representative for International Trade and Investment”.

