00:10:28.650 --> 00:10:33.420
It was a special “honourable” position for a member of the British royal

00:10:33.430 --> 00:10:39.000
family, where the purpose was to represent British business interests abroad.

00:10:40.070 --> 00:10:45.680
In practice, it involved flying around the world, shaking people’s hands, cutting

00:10:45.680 --> 00:10:50.930
ribbons and standing next to business people and politicians for photo opportunities.

00:10:52.250 --> 00:10:57.300
These were all things that Prince Andrew should have been uniquely qualified

00:10:57.310 --> 00:11:02.310
to do, but it turned out that he wasn’t particularly good at this job.

00:11:03.500 --> 00:11:08.600
