00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:13.860
and back home he was accused of everything from being easy to trick with

00:11:14.100 --> 00:11:19.170
fine wine and expensive gifts through to aiding and abetting corruption.

00:11:20.200 --> 00:11:25.110
The position itself was an unpaid one, but he was criticised

00:11:25.360 --> 00:11:29.730
for the huge expense bills that he racked up everywhere he went.

00:11:31.150 --> 00:11:39.950
