00:15:05.569 --> 00:15:09.779
the king’s brother will ever come to anything, whether he will ever have

00:15:09.779 --> 00:15:14.559
to face his accuser in court, much less spend a moment in a jail cell.

00:15:15.579 --> 00:15:22.649
